{"word":"G3853 - παραγγέλλω - parangéllō - par-ang-gel'-lo - Charge","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραγγέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parangéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ang-gel'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Charge</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டளையிடு, கற்பி, கட்டளைக்கொடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to transmit a message along from one to another"},{"paragraph":"2. to command, to order, to charge"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G32 - ἄγγελος - ángelos - ang'-el-os/32\">G32</a>; to <i>transmit a message</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>enjoin:</i> - (give in) charge, (give) command (-ment), declare.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3852/3852\">G3852</a>, <a href=\"#/G3853/3853\">G3853</a>"}]}